<view class="hui-txt-tips">
  <view class="flex hui-flex-align-center">
    <image src="/taofang-package/img/icon-tips.png" mode="scaleToFill"></image>
    <view>请输入您的真实资料用于认证</view>
  </view>
</view>
<form bindsubmit="formSubmit">
  <view class="hui-form-1">
    <view class="hui-form-1-item flex hui-flex-align-center">
      <label>姓名</label>
      <view class="hui-form-input flex-item">
        <input placeholder-style="color:#ccc;font-size:30rpx;" placeholder="请输入姓名"></input>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="hui-form-1-item flex hui-flex-align-center">
      <label>身份证</label>
      <view class="hui-form-input flex-item">
        <input placeholder-style="color:#ccc;font-size:30rpx;" placeholder="请输入身份证号码"></input>
      </view>
    </view>
    <button form-type="submit">立即提交</button>
  </view>
</form>
<view class="hui-description">
  <view class="size-30 black-font">为什么要实名认证？</view>
  <view style="margin-top:25rpx;">使用芝麻实名认证有助于平台对虚假房源的甄别，提高您的房源信息 审核准确性和效率。个人信息仅用于本平台认证，请放心使用。</view>
</view>